[[湾区捷运|湾区捷运]] (BART) 的[[重型鐵路系統|重轨]][[铁道机车车辆|铁道机车车辆]]分为4个单独订单，共计有662<ref name=BartCars2015 >{{cite news |last=Chinn |first=Jerold |date=January 29, 2015 |title=Long wait ahead for longer BART trains |url=http://sfbay.ca/2015/01/29/long-wait-expected-for-longer-bart-trains/ |location=San Francisco Bay Area |quote=BART explains it has total of 662 trains, but about 535 are in service during peak commute times, about 86.5 percent of its fleet. BART said it runs more of its fleet than any other major transit agency despite having the oldest trains in the nation. |access-date=2015-09-29 |archive-date=2020-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203163311/https://sfbay.ca/2015/01/29/long-wait-expected-for-longer-bart-trains/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>节[[电力动车组|电力动车组]]。为确保典型早高峰的正常运营，湾区捷运需要 579 节车辆。其中的535节用于正常服务，剩下的用于组建四组闲置列车组（对于维护准点运营来说是有必要的）。<ref name=BartCars2015/><ref name=crush/> 在任意时刻，剩下的90节车将处于维修，维护或是其他安排了的修改工作。<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.bart.gov/news/articles/2008/news20080924a.aspx |title = "Why can't the trains be longer?" Some background to explain |publisher = BART |date = September 25, 2008 |accessdate = August 23, 2009 |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090827042012/http://www.bart.gov/news/articles/2008/news20080924a.aspx |archivedate = 2009-08-27 |deadurl = no }}</ref>所有在独立的[[競技場－奧克蘭國際機場線|競技場－奧克蘭國際機場線]]线的列车都在没有间隙地运营。[[庞巴迪运输|庞巴迪运输]]正在制造当前列车组的完整替代列车组，第一辆10节编组的新车已于2018年投入运营，预计余下的列车将在2022年到位。届时，在新车到位、旧车淘汰后，将有总计775节列车，长期目标将最终达到1,081节列车。即将到来的{{link-en|eBART|spur line}}列车将会使用[[柴聯車|柴油动车组]]。

主线的[[轨距|轨距]]是{{convert|5|ft|6|in|mm|0}}，宽于近乎通用的[[標準鐵軌|标准轨距]] {{convert|4|ft|8+1/2|in|mm|0}} 。它也使用了平边轨道，而不是通常使用的、角度稍向内倾斜的轨道。这些因素导致湾区捷运需要定制的轮组、刹车系统和轨道维护系统，使维护变得复杂。<ref>{{cite news |title=Has BART's cutting-edge 1972 technology design come back to haunt it? |last=Gafni |first=Matthias |work=San Jose Mercury News |date=March 25, 2016 |url=http://www.mercurynews.com/ci_29687067/has-barts-cutting-edge-1972-technology-design-come.html |accessdate=March 28, 2016 |archive-date=2016-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816065512/http://www.mercurynews.com/ci_29687067/has-barts-cutting-edge-1972-technology-design-come.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>列车的站台高度约为 {{convert|42|in|mm|0}}。{{citation needed|date=May 2016}} 一个能完整进入站台的列车组长度为10节，约 {{convert|710|ft|m|0}} (假设A型车在最尾端)。 而奥克兰机场线使用了由{{link-en|DCC Doppelmayr Cable Car|DCC Doppelmayr|d=多贝玛亚}}公司开发的、现成的{{link-en|Cable Liner|Cable Liner}}整体化[[纜索鐵路|缆车]]技术。
