=== 翻新 ===
在C2型车引入之前，所有车辆的座位和地毯地板都是棕色的。1995年，湾区捷运与[[Adtranz|安达]]（被[[庞巴迪运输|庞巴迪运输]]收购）签订合同，对439辆原装A型和B型车进行翻新，将旧的棕色布料座椅更新为更安全、更易于清洁<ref>{{cite web
 |url          = http://www.bart.gov/news/articles/2015/news20150102
 |title        = New seats now in all trains
 |publisher    = Bay Area Rapid Transit (BART)
 |date         = January 2, 2015
 |accessdate   = December 28, 2015
 |deadurl      = no
 |archive-date = 2021-01-23
 |archive-url  = https://web.archive.org/web/20210123212322/https://www.bart.gov/news/articles/2015/news20150102
}}</ref>的浅蓝色聚氨酯座椅，并将老车改为与C2型车相同的内饰。该项目于2002年完成。A，B和C类车辆原本都被赋予3位数字的编号，翻新后，每辆车编号前都被加了数字1（例如，车辆633将变为1633）。 C2型车被编号为2500系列，C/C1型车依旧只有3位数字的编号。

因为最初的设计目标之一是使所有乘客有座位，旧车内站立乘客的设施例如扶手杆较少。在2010年左右，湾区捷运开始翻新一些C2型车，增加手环和放置行李、轮椅和自行车的区域，后推广到到A，B和C1类车。

2012年之前，所有的列车都装有软垫座椅。据报道，在2011年，列车的座椅上发现了几种[[霉菌|霉菌]]和包括来自粪便的细菌，甚至杀菌剂也无能为力。<ref>Elinson, Zusha (March 5, 2011). [http://www.baycitizen.org/transportation/story/bart-seats-bacteria-blossom/1/ "BART Seats: Where Bacteria Blossom"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.baycitizen.org/transportation/story/bart-seats-bacteria-blossom/1/ |date=20110309083104 }}. ''Bay Citizen''. Accessed March 8, 2011.</ref> 4月，湾区捷运宣布将在下一年花费200万美元来更换脏的座椅，<ref>Elinson, Zusha (April 12, 2011). [https://www.baycitizen.org/news/transportation/bart-spend-2-million-replace-seats/ "BART Plans to Spend $2 Million to Replace Grimy Seats"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.baycitizen.org/news/transportation/bart-spend-2-million-replace-seats/ |date=20140715210324 }}. ''Bay Citizen''. Accessed April 13, 2011.</ref> 并采用更容易清洁的乙烯基表面<ref>{{cite news |first=Zusha |last=Elinson |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/04/06/us/bart-introduces-its-new-vinyl-covered-seats.html |title=BART’s New Seats (a Few) Make Debut |newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |date=April 6, 2012 |accessdate=January 24, 2015 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126132539/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/04/06/us/bart-introduces-its-new-vinyl-covered-seats.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。这一翻新于2014年12月完成。<ref name="seat_replaced">{{cite web |url=http://www.bart.gov/news/articles/2015/news20150102 |title=New seats now in all trains |publisher=Bay Area Rapid Transit (BART) |date=January 2, 2015 |accessdate=January 24, 2015 |archive-date=2021-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123212322/https://www.bart.gov/news/articles/2015/news20150102 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

最初所有的车都铺有地毯。由于类似的问题，所有的地毯已被拆除。<ref>{{cite web|title=BART carpet: Like wool seats, another relic gone for good|url=http://www.bart.gov/news/articles/2015/news20150810-0|website=bart.gov|publisher=Bay Area Rapid Transit (BART)|accessdate=11 April 2016|date=10 August 2015|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123213449/https://www.bart.gov/news/articles/2015/news20150810-0|dead-url=no}}</ref>A型，B型和C2型车现在使用灰色或蓝色的乙烯基地板，而C1型车使用喷涂复合地板。

=== 牵引电机 ===
翻新之前<ref>{{cite news |url = http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20031009005737/en/BART-Renovation-Nears-Completion#.VMSAx8bv2A0 |title = BART Renovation Nears Completion |newspaper = Business Wire |date = October 9, 2003 |accessdate = January 24, 2014 |archive-date = 2019-04-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190404224517/https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20031009005737/en/BART-Renovation-Nears-Completion#.VMSAx8bv2A0 |dead-url = no }}</ref>，在439列 A/B类车上使用的是1463型直流牵引电机，配备了[[西屋公司|西屋]]公司的[[斩波器|斩波器]]。 翻新后，A/B型列车使用了安达（現為龐巴迪）开发的、具有[[絕緣柵雙極晶體管|绝缘栅双极晶体管]]（IGBT）逆变器的1507C型三相交流牵引电机。西屋的电机仍在C1和C2型车上使用，而从A/B型车上拆下的那些则留作备用。

列车的启动加速度为{{convert|3.0|mph/s|abbr=on}}，并且能够保持到{{convert|31|mph}}。在 {{convert|80|mph}}的残余加速度为 {{convert|0.78|mph/s|km/h/s|abbr=on|disp=or}}。制动速度范围是{{convert|0.45 - 3.0|mph/s|km/h/s|abbr=on}}（紧急情况下）。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://faculty.ist.unomaha.edu/winter/publications/2001/Bay_Area_Rapid_Transit_District_Advanced_Automated_Train_Control_System_Case_Study_Description.pdf |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-12-04 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304130439/http://faculty.ist.unomaha.edu/winter/publications/2001/Bay_Area_Rapid_Transit_District_Advanced_Automated_Train_Control_System_Case_Study_Description.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在大修之前，A/B类车上的[[暖通空調|暖通空调]]系统由{{link-en|Thermo King|Thermo King}}（{{link-en|Ingersoll Rand|Ingersoll Rand}}的子公司）制造。在翻新的A/B类车上的空调系统由{{link-en|Westcode|Westcode}}（可能还有[[ADtranz|ADtranz]]）建造。<ref>{{cite web|title=WESTCODE, INC.,  Plaintiff,  v. DAIMLER CHRYSLER RAIL SYSTEMS (NORTH AMERICA) INC., f/k/a AEG TRANSPORTATION SYSTEMS, INC.,  Defendant.|url=https://www.paed.uscourts.gov/documents/opinions/00D0876P.pdf|access-date=2016-12-04|archive-date=2020-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020041506/http://www.paed.uscourts.gov/documents/opinions/00D0876P.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 噪音 ===
许多乘客曾抱怨地铁的噪音。2010年[[旧金山纪事报|旧金山纪事报]]的调查，测量在[[跨灣隧道|跨湾隧道]]的运行噪音高达100[[分貝|分贝]]（相当于手提钻），在其他23个地方也超过90分贝，<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.sfgate.com/bayarea/article/Noise-on-BART-How-bad-is-it-and-is-it-harmful-3175757.php|title=Noise on BART: How bad is it and is it harmful?|last=Cabanatuan|first=Michael|date=2010-09-07|website=SFGate|access-date=2016-04-22|archive-date=2016-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160501181857/http://www.sfgate.com/bayarea/article/Noise-on-BART-How-bad-is-it-and-is-it-harmful-3175757.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>被形容为“女鬼的声音、尖叫的猫头鹰和《[[異世奇人|异世奇人]]》中失控的[[TARDIS|时光机]]”。<ref name=":1" />

然而，当时的发言人却表示，湾区捷运的的噪音平均值为70-80分贝，低于危险水平。根据[[美国国家科学院|美国国家科学院]]1997年的一项研究，湾区捷运被列为全国最安静的运输系统之一。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bart.gov/sites/default/files/docs/noisereport.pdf |author=Nelson, J. T |title=TCRP Report 23: Wheel–Rail Noise Control Manual. |publisher=National Research Council |location=Washington, D.C. |year=1997 |accessdate=September 22, 2015 |archive-date=2017-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170125211642/https://www.bart.gov/sites/default/files/docs/noisereport.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="on20101024">[http://oaklandnorth.net/2010/10/24/why-is-bart-so-noisy/ ''Oakland North Radio''] {{Wayback|url=http://oaklandnorth.net/2010/10/24/why-is-bart-so-noisy/ |date=20201129104505 }}, October 24, 2010. Accessed April 10, 2012.</ref>
[[File:BART_C-car_control_panel.jpg|链接=https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:BART_C-car_control_panel.jpg]]

急弯的噪音是由车轮沿轨道滑动引起的。这种滑动还引起噪声和称为{{link-en|波纹|Washboarding}}的表面损伤。噪声和波纹发生的过程是：<ref name="on20101024" />

# 成对的轮子用轴彼此附接，使它们的旋转速度相同，但在弯道上，外轮和内轮有速度差，导致一边车轮会沿着轨道滑动。
